{"tid":831040,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［Red Bull Air Race］香港機師蔣霆 奧地利站兩連冠創歷史 現Challenger Class排名第一","createTime":"2018-09-21T15:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T15:56:00.000Z","uid":89046,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0c5f17594fbf8dd4ff96b8d4df4ce7dfab639812","tid":831040,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T15:21:46.000Z","msg":"【AIR RACE飛行大賽】香港機師蔣霆奧地利站兩連冠創歷史<br />\n體路 SEPTEMBER 17, 2018<br />\n<br />\n【體路專訊】來自香港的首位Red Bull Air Race World Championship機師蔣霆再次為賽事寫下新的歷史！他在奥地利維也納新城兩天内赢得兩站挑戰組冠軍，令原來總成績排名榜尾的他躍升至榜首位置，同時成為Red Bull Air Race World Championship歷史上首位在連續兩天兩場賽事均贏得冠軍的機師。波蘭的Luke Czepiela在第二場賽事獲得第二名，法國的Baptiste Vignes重複周六成绩獲得第三名。<br />\n<br />\n在奧地利維也納新城的首天賽事，蔣霆排第3出賽。由於Daniel Ryfa以及 Baptiste Vignes都出現失誤被罰時，蔣霆只要沒有失誤就可以肯定站上頒獎台，結果他以1分03秒396的時間贏得冠軍。周日，蔣霆儘管排第一出賽，但他在壓力下仍能以1分03秒654完成，比週六的比賽只差四分之一秒。 Czepiela落後0.253秒，而Vignes則以1分04秒198取得第3名。<br />\n<br />\n蔣霆表示：「保持穩定的飛行及避免失誤是我的目標，雖然我仍有空間可以做出更快的時間，但總的來說，我很滿意自己的表現。在這個周末之，我不確定自己是否有機會參加本賽季的決賽，所以一直只希望在這兩場比賽取勝，以保證能獲得決賽的資格。」今年才是他參加Red Bull Air Race World Championship的第二個賽季，蔣霆的父母亦專程到維也納觀戰。他說：「昨天是他們第一次親自聽到國歌，這真的很特別。我很驚訝自己今天能再次踏上冠軍的頒獎台！」<br />\n<br />\nRed Bull Air Race World Championship下一站將會移師美國。挑戰組的前六名機師將被晉級11月的決賽，在此以前，各機師只剩下一場比賽仍可爭奪積分。憑藉奧地利兩場冠軍，蔣霆在排名榜上飆升至第一位，與第二位Czepiela 同得26分。 法國的Baptiste Vignes在奧地利站的兩個季軍讓他在排行榜上升上第三（22分），至於排名第四的是兩屆挑戰組亞軍、瑞典的Daniel Ryfa（20分）。第五位的是德國兩屆挑戰組冠軍Florian Berger（18分），他在維也納新城賽事輪空，未有參賽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sportsroad.hk/archives/220552\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportsroad.hk%2Farchives%2F220552&d=QQtiiHtHPGfy5ZIUJ8VLOMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=bb202a5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sportsroad.hk/archives/220552</a>"},{"pid":"0afab5ced1a092e0db0cadf82ab806fb812f6ad2","tid":831040,"uid":89046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T15:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/232326_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F232326_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a2e123f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCheck out Wiener Neustadt Challenger Cup recap<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.redbull.tv/video/AP-1V5WRCU312111/wiener-neustadt-challenger-cup-recap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redbull.tv%2Fvideo%2FAP-1V5WRCU312111%2Fwiener-neustadt-challenger-cup-recap&d=QQtiiHtHPGfy5ZIUJ8VLOMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=78338dee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.redbull.tv/video/AP-1V5WRCU312111/wiener-neustadt-challenger-cup-recap</a> <br />\n#redbulltv <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb038277823bbd091b993d4830f55482cdff2fd","tid":831040,"uid":89046,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T15:31:51.000Z","msg":"What it takes to fly in the Red Bull Air Race<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-1FSeUhaoeM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-1FSeUhaoeM&d=QQtiiHtHPGfy5ZIUJ8VLOMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=64cdde79\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-1FSeUhaoeM</a>"},{"pid":"3ba6f0c65867ab3b166f08bd027503eb70e42938","tid":831040,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T23:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6252b94084264612fc08cd71e76ade7551b36e0d","tid":831040,"uid":159236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T00:13:51.000Z","msg":"嘩要推"},{"pid":"0933b0facf1fa39ce5cd20b86157c60b00df553e","tid":831040,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:22:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c8d80fd3f5e7fe432b61e10d9401e2fa12e1b9","tid":831040,"uid":21136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:36:30.00